Issue 本文「### 3.2 `HistoryPane.tsx` で state 追加・localStorage 連携」のコードブロックを、親持ち+props 伝播パターンに修正する:

```diff
-#### 3.2 `HistoryPane.tsx` で state 追加・localStorage 連携
+#### 3.2 親 (`WorktreeDetailRefactored.tsx`) で state + localStorage を持ち、`HistoryPane` に props 伝播
+
+既存の `showArchived` (Issue #168) / `historyDisplayLimit` (Issue #701) と同じ親持ちパターンに揃える:
+
+```ts
+// WorktreeDetailRefactored.tsx（showArchived の直下に追加）
+const [historyUserOnly, setHistoryUserOnly] = useState<boolean>(() => {
+  if (typeof window === 'undefined') return false;
+  return localStorage.getItem(HISTORY_USER_ONLY_STORAGE_KEY) === '1';
+});
+const handleHistoryUserOnlyChange = useCallback((next: boolean) => {
+  setHistoryUserOnly(next);
+  try {
+    localStorage.setItem(HISTORY_USER_ONLY_STORAGE_KEY, next ? '1' : '0');
+  } catch {
+    /* localStorage unavailable */
+  }
+}, []);
+```
+
+```ts
+// HistoryPane.tsx Props に追加（既存 showArchived/historyDisplayLimit と同形）
+export interface HistoryPaneProps {
+  // ...既存
+  /** Issue #725: User only filter state */
+  historyUserOnly?: boolean;
+  /** Issue #725: Callback when User only toggle changes */
+  onHistoryUserOnlyChange?: (userOnly: boolean) => void;
+}
+```
```

